title: Roni Size & Reprazent - New Forms UK Release
description:
New Forms is a 1997 album by the drum and bass act, Roni Size/Reprazent. It was the winner of the Mercury Music Prize in 1997,[1] and often cited as their magnum opus.[2] This album went 5 times platinum.


[edit] Track listing
The original UK version features only disc one[3], with the US release featuring extra content on the second disc.[4]
